50|$|<b>Deposit</b> <b>insurance</b> {{was formed}} to protect small unit banks in the United States when {{branching}} regulations existed. Banks were restricted by location thus did not reap the benefits coming from economies of scale, namely pooling and netting. To protect local banks in poorer states, the <b>federal</b> government created <b>deposit</b> <b>insurance.</b>|$|R
